<p>I’m younger than that now</p>
<p>如今才风华正茂</p>
<p>要实现唱每行歌词的功能，可以通过</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">"Ahh, but I was so much older then"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">"I'm younger than that now"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>又因为这两句歌词为副歌，会反复出现，于是，我们想把这一段代码打包成为一个小的模块去实现</p>
<p>函数：本质上就是一种将实现某种功能的代码进行整理与打包</p>
<p>比如说：</p>
<p>本质上就是我们调用（Calling） Java自带的函数</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">System.out.println(ScreenShows);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>把你要重复调用的内容放在function里面：</p>
<p>1.定义（definition）</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">repeat</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//在my back pages 里面的重复歌词（副歌部分）</span></span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">"Ahh, but I was so much older then"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	System.out.println(<span class="string">"I'm younger than that now"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>2.调用函数（calling）</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repeat();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
