    <url>/2019/08/26/2.Java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>2.Java基础语法</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * This is a example made by William</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * 这个是William的代码示例</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> our_first_package; <span class="comment">// 包 以及这个包的名称</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Hello</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"> * public: access modifier（访问修饰符)/  公共场所（与私人场所对应）</span><br><span class="line"> * 			也就是说，大家都能访问</span><br><span class="line"> * class: 类  /可以把类理解成容器，“人以类聚，物以群分”，一个班的人放到一个教室里面</span><br><span class="line"> * Hello: 类的名字，<span class="number">1</span>.类的名字的文件名字要一致 <span class="number">2</span>.Hello,第一个字母大写！HelloWorld,（NiHao）多个单词的情况下，每个单词首字母大写</span><br><span class="line"> */</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> *小括号（） 一般是在方法（函数）后面</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * 大括号&#123;&#125; 代码块 blocks</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment">/* public: access modifier（访问修饰符)/  公共场所（与私人场所对应）</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> * 为了Java runtime能够去执行，所以需要是公共的，如果不是public，则不能被任何程序运行</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> * </span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> * static（静态）：JVM(Java的虚拟机)会把我们写的class（类）去加载到memory（内存）里面，所以main method主要的方法必须是静态的</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> * 假设你删去了static的时候，会报错：</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> * 错误: main 方法不是类 Hello 中的static, 请将 main 方法定义为:</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> *  public static void main(String[] args)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> *但是这个翻译太烂了，根本看不懂，看我这个版本的：</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> *Main method is not static in class Hello, please define the main method as : </span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> * public static void main(String[] args)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> * </span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> * void:Java设计的时候就有一系列的规定，其中有一个规定每一个method（方法）必须要确定一种返回形式（类型），因为main这个方法并不返回任何东西，所以return type(返回形式)是void这种形式。</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> * 不能删去void,否则编译无法通过</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment"> */</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">	</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">	</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">	</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		System.out.print();</span><br><span class="line">		System.out.println(<span class="string">"2.欢迎来到Java的世界"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//	ctl+/ 就是快速comment写注释的方法1，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//	ctl+shift+/也是一种快速comment写注释的方法2</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">	 * 花括号框起来的 叫做方法的主体部分body of the method()，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">	 * 也就相当于你要执行什么代码的主体</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">	 */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//	program statements是按照什么样的语法进行编写的呢？</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//选择一个object对象，然后说明你要对他实行/实施什么样的method方法，具体方法里面将parameter参数写入 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//system.out 作为一个整体object对象,对他进行println这样方法的操作，println操作的参数为"欢迎来到Java的世界"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//在eclipse里面运行你程序的方法run as java application,先同时按下alt+shift+x(x为执行的意思)，再按下j</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * public class ClassName &#123; public static void main(String[] args) &#123; program</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * statements &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>乐学偶得版权所有  公众号：乐学Fintech  正版视频课程 网易云课堂：乐学偶得</p>
]]></content>
